> Welcome to the experiment!
> In this experiment, you will be asked to make judgments about the content of different sentences.
> On each trial, you will read a sentence, and will be shown a picture immediately following the sentence.
> Your task is to decide whether the object displayed in the picture was mentioned in the sentence or not
> and respond as quickly as possible by pressing S for yes or N for no.
> You will now do a practice session with feedback and instructions.
> Click the button below to continue.
